01:05:50,960 --> 01:05:54,240
All right. If it's a fight you want,
a fight you'll get.

735
01:06:21,720 --> 01:06:24,160
Damn you. You're gonna pay for that.

736
01:07:11,760 --> 01:07:13,240
Shut up!

737
01:07:13,720 --> 01:07:16,160
Will you two morons, knock it off!

738
01:07:16,200 --> 01:07:19,040
We've got an international incident
going on here!

739
01:07:22,320 --> 01:07:24,640
-I knew you'd come.
-Ja, danke.

740
01:07:24,800 --> 01:07:28,120
-You may thank Mrs. Feldman.
-Who is Mrs. Feldman?

741
01:07:28,240 --> 01:07:31,400
You know Mrs. Feldman,
a member of the defunct C.O.P. team.

742
01:07:38,240 --> 01:07:40,960
This is Sgt. Mahoney
in pursuit of a stolen police car.

743
01:07:40,960 --> 01:07:43,040
I'm headed towards
the Williams County air show.

744
01:07:43,160 --> 01:07:47,160
Repeat, I'm pursing four escapees
toward the Williams County air show.

745
01:07:47,720 --> 01:07:49,800
Now, folks,
making his second appearance...

746
01:07:49,920 --> 01:07:53,160
at the Williams County air show....

747
01:08:02,800 --> 01:08:05,000
-Look out for that car!
-What car?

748
01:08:06,240 --> 01:08:08,560
That car! Come on, get out!

749
01:08:10,320 --> 01:08:11,560
Come on!

750
01:08:12,800 --> 01:08:14,560
Let's get out of here!

751
01:08:16,400 --> 01:08:17,760
Hurry up!

752
01:09:05,200 --> 01:09:08,640
This is where I draw the line.
I'm not going up in one of those things.

753
01:09:08,760 --> 01:09:11,640
-No way. No, sirree.
-You don't have to.

754
01:09:34,320 --> 01:09:36,200
You can open your eyes now.

755
01:09:36,760 --> 01:09:39,360
How can you like this
better than my driving?

756
01:09:39,400 --> 01:09:42,640
Because you can't do this in a car.

757
01:10:00,160 --> 01:10:01,560
Grab that balloon!

758
01:10:02,720 --> 01:10:05,000
We commandeer this balloon
in the name of the law!

759
01:10:05,160 --> 01:10:08,720
-No, wait, you can't!
-You can't do that. We need it for the race.

760
01:10:19,120 --> 01:10:23,520
Mrs. Feldman, stay with the car.
Zed, Sweetchuck, follow me.

761
01:10:25,960 --> 01:10:28,720
Guys, wait up! Tackleberry.

762
01:10:29,960 --> 01:10:31,600
-What do I pull?
-Take it up!

763
01:10:31,760 --> 01:10:35,040
-They're getting away! Let's go!
-We are going up, sir.

764
01:10:41,400 --> 01:10:44,760
Come on! Drop the parachute!

765
01:10:45,560 --> 01:10:47,000
Stop screwing around!

766
01:10:47,920 --> 01:10:51,000
-Come on! Drop the parachute!
-Come on!

767
01:10:51,120 --> 01:10:53,720
If he doesn't want to do it, don't push him.

768
01:10:53,840 --> 01:10:56,040
He's gotta, like, wanna help himself.

769
01:11:02,920 --> 01:11:05,120
You land that balloon right now!

770
01:11:05,400 --> 01:11:08,760
This is Capt. Harris! You are under arrest!

771
01:11:08,800 --> 01:11:11,400
Land that balloon now!

772
01:11:13,840 --> 01:11:17,320
-I'll just blast them out of the sky, sir.
-No! Not yet.

773
01:11:17,960 --> 01:11:21,120
You're right.
I should give them a warning shot first.

774
01:11:26,200 --> 01:11:29,240
lmbecile! Are you happy now?

775
01:11:29,760 --> 01:11:32,240
At least it looks like
we're coming down in the river.

776
01:11:32,360 --> 01:11:35,800
It won't matter
because you're going to be dead!

777
01:11:35,960 --> 01:11:37,040
Pretty view--

778
01:11:41,560 --> 01:11:43,920
I hate water!

779
01:11:47,920 --> 01:11:49,000
Help!

780
01:11:53,360 --> 01:11:56,640
-They're in the river.
-Hurry. Maybe we can catch them.

781
01:12:00,120 --> 01:12:02,560
I'll pull alongside Tackleberry.

782
01:12:07,520 --> 01:12:09,840
Look, I see my house!

783
01:12:10,520 --> 01:12:12,000
Look, the crooks!

784
01:12:14,200 --> 01:12:16,120
Let's go get them, okay?

785
01:12:29,040 --> 01:12:30,400
Hang on, sir!

786
01:12:34,640 --> 01:12:37,640
-Hurry, before they go over the falls!
-There they go!

787
01:12:40,840 --> 01:12:42,160
Get a rope!

788
01:12:43,200 --> 01:12:45,040
Hang on. Hang on, sir!

789
01:12:47,560 --> 01:12:49,720
Hang on, we'll come and get you!

790
01:12:56,960 --> 01:12:58,000
Grab it!

791
01:13:18,400 --> 01:13:19,800
Try to relax!

792
01:13:31,960 --> 01:13:34,960
There's the balloon! Now I've got them.

793
01:13:45,960 --> 01:13:50,240
There's only one way to do this
and it's up to me!

794
01:13:51,440 --> 01:13:55,040
-Take over!
-He was talking to you!

795
01:13:55,840 --> 01:13:58,440
If you're coming back, bring some beer!

796
01:14:06,640 --> 01:14:10,120
-No. He was talking to you.
-No, I heard him.

797
01:14:10,240 --> 01:14:14,520
-He said, "Sweetchuck, take over."
-No, he did not.

798
01:14:17,640 --> 01:14:20,800
-Get off of my foot!
-Shut up! Why are you always whining?

799
01:14:20,960 --> 01:14:22,600
Leave me alone!

800
01:14:51,800 --> 01:14:55,400
Gentlemen, may I see your license
and registration, please?

801
01:14:56,320 --> 01:15:01,000
There they are. Take it down.
I want to get close. Get closer.

802
01:15:05,240 --> 01:15:08,240
Mahoney, what are you doing?

803
01:15:08,640 --> 01:15:10,040
Get in closer!

804
01:15:22,720 --> 01:15:24,840
What do you think you're doing?

805
01:15:29,360 --> 01:15:31,440
I'll take care of you, copper!

806
01:15:32,560 --> 01:15:35,160
Get off my wing! Get off of there!

807
01:15:35,200 --> 01:15:37,200
What will you do about them?

808
01:15:44,160 --> 01:15:47,360
Pal, it's over. Let's go home.

809
01:15:50,120 --> 01:15:53,400
-I hate you.
-I'm not really thrilled about you!

810
01:15:54,040 --> 01:15:57,800
-Why don't you lose some weight?
-Why don't you get out and walk?

811
01:16:00,760 --> 01:16:03,720
-I'm going to be sick!
-I don't have a parachute!

812
01:16:03,960 --> 01:16:07,760
-Shut up! I'm going to be sick!
-Don't be sick on me!

813
01:16:17,960 --> 01:16:20,840
-I don't have a chute!
-Break your fall!

814
01:16:20,960 --> 01:16:24,000
-Hit the kids!
-No, I need a chute!

815
01:16:24,360 --> 01:16:26,160
Get your own! Get away from me!

816
01:16:26,200 --> 01:16:27,840
Come on!

817
01:16:28,800 --> 01:16:29,920
Let go!

818
01:16:30,560 --> 01:16:32,800
I'll break you in half, you dweeb.

819
01:16:32,920 --> 01:16:36,320
There, I opened the chute.
Are you satisfied? Leave me alone!

820
01:16:42,120 --> 01:16:45,400
-I'm going to kill you!
-Shut up and enjoy the flight!

821
01:16:55,360 --> 01:16:56,760
Get off me!

822
01:17:02,920 --> 01:17:06,120
Commandant, they say
your Citizens On Patrol group...

823
01:17:06,240 --> 01:17:10,200
does many, many
wonderful and crazy things.

824
01:17:18,560 --> 01:17:22,160
I think Sgt. Mahoney
deserves a special bow.

825
01:17:22,560 --> 01:17:24,200
-Mahoney?
-All right!

826
01:17:25,160 --> 01:17:26,960
-Mahoney?
-Way to go!

827
01:17:36,560 --> 01:17:38,040
Get up! Look, it's Mahoney!

828
01:17:38,160 --> 01:17:39,960
-Where?
-Sorry.

829
01:17:44,640 --> 01:17:46,840
-To the Academy.
-To the Academy.

830
01:17:53,560 --> 01:17:56,560
You know, you look
a little like Tom Cruise in Top Gun.

831
01:17:56,600 --> 01:17:58,360
-Yeah?
-No!